item.title: Greetings
item.description: and there it is… Hi there! I got it! Finally. This is my first post, nothing more than an introduction and a chance to say hello! I hope to provide fun and useful news, topic and subjects here. I am pretty new on blogging so I will do my best. I want to thank everyone will take some time to check it and give it a read. I will update my twitter account every time a new post will be released so, don’t forget to follow me at @DeadCip
